      "text": "Why did the gateway fail?\nLet me check the logs.\n\n> The gateway likely crashed; inspect the most recent log lines before answering.\n\n**Tool calls:**\n\n```json\n[\n  {\n    \"arguments\": {\n      \"cmd\": \"tail -n 5 gateway.log\"\n    },\n    \"id\": \"call_1\",\n    \"name\": \"terminal\"\n  }\n]\n```\nERROR: bind: address already in use\nThe gateway port is already in use. Stop the other process and restart it.",
